data.description: Welcome to a true masterpiece! Exceptional home! Hard surface flooring thru-out sets stage for a lifestyle of both style & practicality. Haven of culinary delights in chef's dream kitchen, boasting a 5-burner gas stove, double ovens,  sprawling island, spice drawers &  walk-in pantry.  Living & dining spaces offer perfect balance of formal elegance & open, casual living. Spacious family room open to kitchen creates an inviting atmosphere for gatherings. Gas fireplace!! 4 generous bedrooms, each with walk-in closets, private bath or Jack & Jill set up. Split plan for privacy. Game rm or private office. Surround sound! Backyard is vision of style, with travertine flooring, pool with lounge step & H2O feature, Gazebo! Great community with parks, BB courts & fitness trails! Make this HOME!
